description:
10 new cards appear in LogiKing LEVEL2 !!
Keeping the rules simple and deep,
Master the card effects that have evolved and deepened!

Of course, deck composition with new cards of LEVEL2,
It is also possible to play by combining the cards of LogiKing !
Invent your own 10-card deck.

Mastering the 10 new Noble Phantasms,
Prove that you are the LogiKing !


*This content is the same as that included in the "LogiKing LEVEL1 & 2 Special Pack".
*To use this additional content, you need "LogiKing" (sold separately).
*Be sure to update to the latest version before using.
name: LogiKing LEVEL2
